'''馬菲·基克斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Matthew Gilks'''}}，姓氏讀作''Jilks''，{{bd|1982年|6月4日|catIdx=Gilks, Matthew}}）是一名在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生的[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[門將|門將]]，現時效力[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]。他出身家鄉球會[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|羅奇代爾]]，效力7年後於2007年轉投[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，加盟「金絲雀」（''the Canaries''）一個球季而未有獲派在一隊上陣，於2008年作為球員交換被交易到[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，亦曾被短暫借用到[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]。

雖然在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生，但基克斯以[[祖母|祖母]]血緣取得代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]參加國際賽資格，於2010年8月曾獲徵召入伍。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
;羅奇代爾
基克斯在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[西北英格蘭|西北部]][[大曼徹斯特郡|大曼徹斯特郡]][[羅奇代爾|羅奇代爾]]（Rochdale）出生，年僅13歲已加盟家鄉球會[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|羅奇代爾]]的優材中心（Centre of Excellence），於2000年3月由青年隊提升上一隊，直到2001年3月17日才首次於作客1-1賽和[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|車士打菲特]]中上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/1224419.stm |title=Chesterfield 1-1 Rochdale |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2001-03-17 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307175430/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/1224419.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間主要擔任[[Neil_Edwards_(footballer_born_1970)|尼爾·愛華士]]（Neil Edwards）的副手，2004/05年球季兩人合力創出整季有20場不失球的球會新記錄，而其中15場由基克斯把關<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.ex-canaries.co.uk/players/gilks.htm |title=Matthew Gilks |publisher=''ex-canaries.co.uk'' |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104073413/http://www.ex-canaries.co.uk/players/gilks.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終更取代尼爾·愛華士的常規正選席位成為球隊1號門將，於2005/06年及2006/07年兩個球季基克斯出席羅奇代爾整季所有賽事。他為羅奇代爾在聯賽及盃賽合共上陣197場，當他還只是24歲時，已經是隊中效力年期最長的球員<ref name="bbc6245490"/>。

;諾域治
2007年7月1日約滿羅奇代爾的基克斯以[[自由球員|自由身]]轉投[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，簽約兩年<ref name="bbc6245490">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/6245490.stm |title=Norwich to sign Rochdale keeper |date=2007-06-27 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |accessdate=2008-11-21 |archive-date=2013-01-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DbywRpbS?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/6245490.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他未能躋身「金絲雀」（''the Canaries''）一隊陣中，於[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]大部分時間坐於後備席廂<ref name="bbc7741834">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/7741834.stm |title=Gilks solves Shrews keeper crisis |date=2008-11-21 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |accessdate=2008-11-21 |archive-date=2013-01-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DbyxXK7J?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/7741834.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間更於2007年11月在操練時扭傷[[足踝|足踝]]導致[[韌帶|韌帶]]受創而缺席一段時間<ref name="bbc7121044">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/7121044.stm |title=Gilks looks set for rapid return |date=2007-11-30 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |accessdate=2008-11-21}}</ref>。

;黑池
2008年6月26日諾域治證實以球員加現金收購[[韦斯·荷拉汉|韦斯·荷拉汉]]，而基克斯則反方向加盟[[黑池足球會|黑池]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3742376,00.html |title=Hoolahan makes Canaries switch |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2008-06-26 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2008-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029002820/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3742376,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加盟初期基克斯未能動搖正選門將[[保罗·拉楚布卡|-{zh-hans:保罗·拉楚布卡; zh-hk:拉查布卡;}-]]（Paul Rachubka）的地位，只在季初獲派在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一圈作客[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|馬爾斯菲]]首次上陣，但以0-2落敗被淘汰出局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7541926.stm |title=Macclesfield 2-0 Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-08-12 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2008-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080813010453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7541926.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於缺乏上陣機會，基克斯一度失去信心並想放棄足球轉往工廠或車房工作<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1307375/Matt-Gilks-considered-swapping-football-factory-work.html |title=Last chance: Blackpool stopper Matt Gilks considered swapping football for the factory |publisher=''dailymail.co.uk'' |date=2010-08-30 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524095634/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1307375/Matt-Gilks-considered-swapping-football-factory-work.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，幸好在11月21日獲[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]要求借用1個月以舒緩受傷門將的危機<ref name="bbc7741834"/><ref name="STFC1461894">{{cite web |language=en |title=New Keeper Joins |publisher=[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|''shrewsburytown.com'']] |date=2008-11-21 |url=http://www.shrewsburytown.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10443~1461894,00.html |accessdate=2008-11-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dbz0nWVO?url=http://mobile.shrewsburytown.com/ |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref><ref name="STFC1461949">{{cite web |language=en |title=Matt Gilks |publisher=[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|''shrewsburytown.com'']] |date=2008-11-21 |url=http://www.shrewsburytown.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10443~1461949,00.html |accessdate=2008-11-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dbz2NYFY?url=http://mobile.shrewsburytown.com/ |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref>，他於翌日首次上陣，於開賽不久即有球員被逐僅得10人應戰而力保不失，作客0-0賽和[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7727544.stm |title=Lincoln City 0-0 Shrewsbury |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-11-22 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307160030/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7727544.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他為梳士貝利上陣多3仗才結束借用返回黑池。其時剛好領隊[[西蒙·加利臣|西蒙·加利臣]]轉投[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，在任期間加利臣習慣出場名單不探用後補門將，而將5個後補名額全數給予場上球員，當他離隊後，看守領隊[[東尼·柏堅斯|東尼·柏堅斯]]（Tony Parkes）隨即開始將基克斯列入後補名單中。

在擔任數場沒有上陣的板凳球員後，他於2009年1月31日獲得上陣機會，其時正選門將[[保罗·拉楚布卡|-{zh-hans:拉楚布卡; zh-hk:拉查布卡;}-]]於作客對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]開賽僅3分鐘便被[[球證|球證]]直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場，基克斯臨危受命力保不失，協助球隊小勝1-0奏凱而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7856654.stm |title=Crystal Palace 0-1 Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-01-31 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2009-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202094840/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7856654.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BFC45460">{{cite web |language=en |title=Report – Crystal Palace vs Blackpool |publisher=[[黑池足球會|''blackpoolfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-01-31 |url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10432~45460,00.html |accessdate=2009-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dbz4aEQx?url=http://mobile.blackpoolfc.co.uk/ |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref>。基克斯在-{zh-hans:拉楚布卡; zh-hk:拉查布卡;}-停賽期間再獲派上陣4場。

[[黑池2009年至2010年球季|2009/10年球季]]基克斯受惠於新任領隊[[伊恩·荷路威|伊恩·荷路威]]（Ian Holloway）的輪換政策而取得更多上陣機會，雖然季初只獲派在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]上陣，他於第三圈作客3-4遭[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]淘汰一仗曾經救出一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8256916.stm |title=Stoke 4-3 Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-09-22 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2009-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925160529/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8256916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年10月17日他獲派首次在本季聯賽上陣，在主場[[布隆菲尔德路球场|布隆菲尔德路球场]]2-0輕取[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8302280.stm |title=Blackpool 2-0 Plymouth |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100128053758/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8302280.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後兩場分別主場以3-0擊敗[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]及作客0-0賽和[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]，連續3仗保持清白之軀，與隊友[[史提芬·格尼|-{zh-hans:斯蒂芬·卡雷尼;zh-hk:格尼}-]]（Stephen Crainey）和[[Marcel_Seip|马塞尔·斯普]]（Marcel Seip）於對史雲斯賽後一同入選「英冠每週最佳陣容」<ref name="bfc1838549">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~1838549,00.html |title=Trio Named In Team Of The Week |date=2009-10-27 |publisher=[[黑池足球會|''blackpoolfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2009-10-27 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="FL147726">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/staticFiles/e/41/0,,10794~147726,00.pdf |title=Championship Team Of The Week (26/10/2009) |date=2009-10-26 |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |accessdate=2009-10-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69puYYmEg?url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/staticFiles/e/41/0,,10794~147726,00.pdf |archivedate=2012-08-11 }}</ref>。2010年2月16日他於主場2-0擊敗[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]再救出一個[[十二碼|十二碼]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8510865.stm |title=Blackpool 2-0 Middlesbrough |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100219011641/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8510865.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨著-{zh-hans:拉楚布卡; zh-hk:拉查布卡;}-的長期傷患，基克斯於2月初開始穩佔首席門將位置。3月6日主場1-0擊敗[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]是他的職業生涯上陣第200場聯賽，更獲選「賽事最佳球員」（Man of the Match）<ref name="bfc47457">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10432~47457,00.html |title=Blackpool vs Ipswich Town |date=2010-03-06 |publisher=[[黑池足球會|''blackpoolfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-03-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dbz7bodQ?url=http://mobile.blackpoolfc.co.uk/ |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref>，他近5場賽事中4場保持不失，賽後再度入選「英冠每週最佳陣容」<ref name="bfc1988418">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~1988418,00.html |title=Gilks In Team Of The Week |date=2010-03-06 |publisher=[[黑池足球會|''blackpoolfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-03-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100310233220/http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~1988418,00.html |archivedate=2010-03-10 }}</ref><ref name="FL150279">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/staticFiles/7/4b/0,,10794~150279,00.pdf |title=Championship Team Of The Week (08/03/2010) |date=2010-03-08 |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |accessdate=2010-03-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331224536/http://www.football-league.co.uk/staticFiles/7/4b/0%2C%2C10794~150279%2C00.pdf |archivedate=2010-03-31 }}</ref>。黑池取得聯賽第6位及最後一個參加升班附加賽名額，準決賽兩回合累計6-4擊敗[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]；2010年5月22日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]舉行的決賽以3-2擊敗[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]取得升班[[英超|英超]]最後一張入場劵<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm |title=Blackpool 3-2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-22 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2012-11-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CN1HtqfI?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。連同3場附加賽，基克斯整季上陣32場賽事。

[[黑池2010年至2011年球季|2010/11年球季]]受傷的-{zh-hans:拉楚布卡; zh-hk:拉查布卡;}-沒有註冊於黑池[[英超|英超]]的25人上陣名單內<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6516292,00.html |title=Holloway admits keeper error |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-11-19 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120201119/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6516292,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，只在季初免費簽入[[迦納國家足球隊|加納]]門將[[李察·京遜|李察·京遜]]作為基克斯的副車<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6353570,00.html |title=Pool pounce for Kingson |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-09-02 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101005215330/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6353570,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年8月14日，基克斯亮相首場[[英超|英超]]賽事作客[[DW運動場|DW運動場]]以4-0大勝[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8904972.stm |title=Wigan 0-4 Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-14 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2012-11-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CN1Ik55A?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8904972.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基克斯的合約將於夏季屆滿，雖然黑池有意提供三年新約，但由於季初出色的表現，加上入選[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國家隊]]，引起多支英超球隊的注目<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6447209,00.html |title=Pool face Gilks struggle |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-10-16 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081644/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6447209,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中包括英超新豪門[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6556742,00.html |title=Gilks eyes Prem switch |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-12-06 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101215202716/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6556742,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月13日作客0-0賽和[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，基克斯半場因傷退下火線<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9175420.stm |title=West Ham 0-0 Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-13 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208081124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9175420.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]髕骨[[骨折|骨折]]，需要養傷最少兩個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/9206450.stm |title=Blackpool dealt Matt Gilks injury blow |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-18 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2010-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121055039/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/9206450.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基克斯傷勢復原的進展比預計緩慢<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6651066,00.html |title=Grandin back to face Liverpool |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110822173813/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6651066,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，骨折雖然癒合，但因大腿內側肌肉損耗（muscle wastage）而導致不能屈曲或移動<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6744451,00.html |title=Pool rocked by Rachubka blow |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-03-30 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917015010/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6744451,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他於缺陣近5個月後才於2011年3月中復出為黑池預備隊把關出戰[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，但僅14分鐘便因拉傷小腿而退下火線<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6815136,00.html |title=Fresh Gilks injury blow |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-03-15 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515193957/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6815136,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基克斯最終在4月16日傷癒復出於主場迎戰護級競爭對手[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]，黑池在這場6分榜末大戰以1-3落敗而跌入降班區域<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9455799.stm |title=Blackpool 1-3 Wigan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-16 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2012-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121142621/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9455799.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
2010年8月22日[[蘇格蘭足球協會|蘇格蘭足球協會]]證實領隊[[奇治·尼雲|-{zh-hans:克雷格·勒韦恩; zh-hant:奇治·尼雲;}-]]（Craig Levein）有意徵召基克斯進入[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國家隊]]備戰對[[立陶宛國家足球隊|立陶宛]]和[[列支敦士登國家足球隊|列支敦士登]]兩場[[2012年歐洲國家盃外圍賽I組|2012年歐洲國家盃外圍賽]]，他以[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]裔的[[祖母|祖母]]而取得入選資格<ref name="sfa6365">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=128&newsID=6365 |title=Gilks can be tartan tower of strength |date=2010-08-22 |publisher=[[蘇格蘭足球協會|''scottishfa.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614220238/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=128&newsID=6365 |archive-date=2011-06-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。兩天後他與隊友[[查理·阿當|查理·阿當]]獲得正式徵召入伍<ref name="bfc2132999">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~2132999,00.html |title=GILKS JOINS CHARLIE IN SCOTLAND SQUAD |date=2010-08-24 |publisher=[[黑池足球會|''blackpoolfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-08-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100826081834/http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~2132999,00.html |archivedate=2010-08-26 }}</ref><ref name="sfa6379">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=128&newsCategoryID=6&newsID=6379 |title=Scotland squad announcement Tuesday, 24 August 2010 |date=2010-08-24 |publisher=[[蘇格蘭足球協會|''scottishfa.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-08-24 |archive-date=2010-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901162802/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=128&newsCategoryID=6&newsID=6379 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於9月7日主場2-1擊敗[[列支敦士登國家足球隊|列支敦士登]]擔任沒有上陣的後補球員<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro2012/matches/season=2012/round=15171/match=2002207/postmatch/lineups/index.html |title=Scotland 2-1 Liechtenstein (Lineups) |publisher=[[UEFA|''uefa.com'']] |date=2010-09-07 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |archive-date=2011-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110819043655/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro2012/matches/season=2012/round=15171/match=2002207/postmatch/lineups/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

